==Recipes==
Ostrich Eggs work the same as regular chicken [[Egg|eggs]] in all recipes.{{#lsth:Egg|Recipes}}
==Tailoring==
Ostrich Egg is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the {{name|Warrior Helmet|class=inline}}.

